author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Echo Polska Posts FY Distributable Income Per Share 10.87 Euro Cents​
text:
March 8 (Reuters) - Echo Polska Properties Nv:
* ‍FY NET ASSET VALUE EXCLUDING DEFERRED TAX TOTALLED EUR927.6 MILLION WITH NAV PER SHARE AT EUR1.32​
* FY ‍DISTRIBUTABLE EARNINGS OF EUR76.60 MILLION​ * FY ‍DISTRIBUTABLE INCOME PER SHARE 10.87 EUR CENTS​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
